l certification in Deep Memory Process must attend the next two advance modules.";s:8:"sbx_type";s:4:"icon";s:17:"service_box_image";s:71:"http://sample-data.kallyas.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/ib-ico-31.svg";s:23:"service_box_image_hover";s:0:"";s:8:"sbx_size";s:2:"40";s:8:"sbx_icon";a:2:{s:6:"family";s:27:"glyphicons_halflingsregular";s:7:"unicode";s:5:"ue171";}s:18:"znpb_hide_visitors";s:3:"all";s:9:"css_class";s:0:"";}s:7:"content";a:0:{}s:5:"width";s:0:"";s:6:"widget";s:0:"";s:3:"uid";s:13:"eluid1b691bc7";}}s:5:"width";s:8:"col-md-6";s:6:"widget";s:0:"";s:3:"uid";s:13:"eluidf4d20a24";}i:2;a:6:{s:6:"object";s:8:"ZnColumn";s:7:"options";a:0:{}s:7:"content";a:1:{i:0;a:6:{s:6:"object";s:13:"TH_ServiceBox";s:7:"options";a:12:{s:9:"sbx_style";s:5:"boxed";s:14:"element_scheme";s:0:"";s:17:"service_box_title";s:24:"Module 3: Advanced Level";s:16:"service_box_desc";s:65:"Physical Body Release including Healing the Energy or Subtle Body";s:20:"service_box_features";s:616:"Working directly with the body, understanding the correct use of touch and props. Inductions into past life memories via the body; understanding chronic physical patterns held at death, giving the various parts of the body have a voice and tell its story. Techniques to ‘unfreeze’ life force energy and help the stuck emotions, thoughts and physical residues be released. Working with the physical Body or postural image; understanding the connection to the wounds held in the etheric body; places of stored emotion in the body; strategies for release of body patterns using props and psycho-dramatic techniques ";s:8:"sbx_type";s:4:"icon";s:17:"service_box_image";s:0:"";s:23:"service_box_image_hover";s:0:"";s:8:"sbx_size";s:2:"40";s:8:"sbx_icon";a:2:{s:6:"family";s:27:"glyphicons_halflingsregular";s:7:"unicode";s:5:"ue067";}s:18:"znpb_hide_visitors";s:3:"all";s:9:"css_class";s:0:"";}s:7:"content";a:0:{}s:5:"width";s:0:"";s:6:"widget";s:0:"";s:3:"uid";s:13:"eluidefc5ffca";}}s:5:"width";s:8:"col-md-6";s:6:"wi