(1502, 1, '2015-09-07 00:33:39', '2015-09-07 00:33:39', '<div class="Normal-P-P7"><span class="Normal-C-C29">Anita speaks about her remarkable near death experience, which took place during what was supposed to be her final hours of life. She felt as though she entered another dimension and was faced with a choice of whether to return to life or not.  Although seemingly in a coma to all who were observing, she experienced heightened awareness of everything that was taking place around her, as well as great clarity and understanding of her life and purpose here on earth.</span><span class="Normal-C-C31">  </span><span class="Normal-C-C29">Anita subsequently chose to return to life when she understood that ‘heaven’ is a state, and not a place. This subsequently led to a remarkable and complete recovery of her health.</span></div>', 'Seeing Through the Veil', 'Annediscusses how current beliefs about death and the censorship of material on non-<wbr />ordinary experiences constrict the human spirit and limit the horizon of our sight. She explores the approach to death of earlier cultures and also the idea of the ‘subtle’ or ‘light’ body that offers us a very different understanding of the survival of the soul. Could it be that the apparent finality of death is the greatest of our illusions? Relinquishing old beliefs can alleviate the trauma of bereavement and give us trust and hope in our survival.', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'seeing-through-the-veil', '', '', '2016-07-17 15:09:14', '2016-07-17 15:09:14', '', 0, 'http://sample-data.kallyas.net/product/kensley-bath-ensemble-in-coral/', 0, 'product', '', 0),
(1504, 1, '2015-09-07 00:36:27', '2015-09-07 00:36:27', '<span class="Normal-C-C29">In this lost teaching the symbol of the Cross is revealed to be more than a sacrificial reference, but holds the secret of the transcendent intersection that unites heaven and earth, spirit and nature, body ;and soul. Then around the cosmic cross is entwined the cosmic Serpent of “great creating Nature” who governs every great world cycle as Aeon, cosmic time.</span><span class="Normal-C-C10">\r\n</span>', 'Mystical Body, Man of Light: The Lost Secret of the Cosmic Christ', 'What sets Christianity apart from most other religions is the Mystery of the Incarnation: that Jesus was both Man and God, and that His Being, as Corpus Christi, rules the whole universe. Behind Saint John’s teaching that “the Word was made flesh” is the cosmic Logos of the Jewish mystic Philo and with it a dazzling array of images of Anthropos or Adam Kadmon, the androgynous Universal or Cosmic Man.', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'mystical-body-man-of-light-the-lost-secret-of-the-cosmic-christ', '', '', '2016-07-17 15:07:16', '2016-07-17 15:07:16', '', 0, 'http://sample-data.kallyas.net/product/grommet-window-curtain-valance/', 0, 'product', '', 0),
(1506, 1, '2015-09-07 00:37:20', '2015-09-07 00:37:20', '<span class="Normal-C-C29">This stimulating and provocative day examined hitherto unexplored questions regarding Jung’s debt to German Romanticism, spiritualism, and Judaism through the eyes of prominent students of his life.\r\n</span><span class="Normal-C-C29">\r\n</span><span class="Normal-C-C29">Conference Introduction: Dr Roger Woolger PhD\r\n</span><span class="Normal-C-C29">\r\n</span><span class="Normal-C-C29">2 lectures:\r\n</span><span class="Normal-C-C29">   •  Jung’s Relationship with Mediumship\r\n</span><span class="Normal-C-C29">  •  Ancestral Shadows -<wbr /> Spirits and Politics in Jung’s Secret life\r\n</span>', 'CG Jung, Goethe & The Politics of the Spirit : Ancestors, Mediums and Lovers', '<span class="Normal-C-C29">This stimulating and provocative day examined hitherto unexplored questions regarding Jung’s debt to German Romanticism, spiritualism, and Judaism through the eyes of prominent students of his life.\r\n</span><span class="Normal-C-C29">\r\n</span><span class="Normal-C-C29">Conference Introduction: Dr Roger Woolger PhD\r\n</span><span class="Normal-C-C29">\r\n</span><span class="Normal-C-C29">2 lectures:\r\n</span><span class="Normal-C-C29">   •  Jung’s Relationship with Mediumship\r\n</span><span class="Normal-C-C29">  •  Ancestral Shadows -<wbr /> Spirits and Politics in Jung’s Secret life\r\n</span>', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'cg-jung-goethe-the-politics-of-the-spirit-ancestors-mediums-and-lovers', '', '', '2016-07-17 15:05:39', '2016-07-17 15:05:39', '', 0, 'http://sample-data.kallyas.net/product/top-down-bottom-up-cordless-cellular/', 0, 'product', '', 0),
(1511, 1, '2015-09-07 00:38:58', '2015-09-07 00:38:58', '<div class="Normal-P-P5"><span class="Emphasis-C">The Holy Grail: Healing the Sexual Wound in the Western Psyche by renowned Jungian psychologist Roger J. Woolger. This would not be Mr.</span><span class="Normal-C-C15">Woolger’s first foray into audio. He has published several with the Sounds True label who also records and distributes Eckhart Tolle among others. With degrees from Oxford and London Universities as well as the C.G. Jung Institute in Zurich, Roger developed a practice of spiritual psychotherapy he terms Deep Memory Process which he use to teach in Europe and the U.S. Roger’s eloquent and clear narration is the perfect vehicle for Jungian thought as well as any classical or philosophical text. Comprehensive ideas are rendered </span><span class="Normal-C-C16">accessible and his heartfelt delivery was as enjoyable to listen to as any welcomed guest.\r\n</span></div>\r\n<div class="Normal-P-P4"><span class="Normal-C-C16"> </span></div>\r\n<div class="Normal-P-P6"><span class="Normal-C-C17">Topics include:  </span><span class="Normal-C-C16">The Troubadors, The Cult of the Lady, The Psychological Significance of Chivalry and Perceval the Hero</span></div>', 'The Holy Grail: Healing the Sexual Wound in the Western Psyche', '”In the following essay I shall attempt to show how we can read the myths and legends of the eleventh and twelfth centuries as the collective dreams of the mid-<wbr />term crisis of the Christian era. As an example of this we will apply C.G. Jung’s method of dream interpretations to the important work to Chretien de Troyes’ version of the Grail legend.” – From the introduction to The Holy Grail: Healing the Sexual Wound in the Western Psyche.', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'the-holy-grail-healing-the-sexual-wound-in-the-western-psyche', '', '', '2016-07-17 15:01:46', '2016-07-17 15:01:46', '', 0, 'http://sample-data.kallyas.net/product/2-inch-faux-wood-blind/', 0, 'product', '', 0),
