(2007, 1, '2016-07-17 15:05:33', '2016-07-17 15:05:33', '<span class="Normal-C-C29">This stimulating and provocative day examined hitherto unexplored questions regarding Jung’s debt to German Romanticism, spiritualism, and Judaism through the eyes of prominent students of his life.\n</span><span class="Normal-C-C29">\n</span><span class="Normal-C-C29">Conference Introduction: Dr Roger Woolger PhD\n</span><span class="Normal-C-C29">\n</span><span class="Normal-C-C29">2 lectures:\n</span><span class="Normal-C-C29">   •  Jung’s Relationship with Mediumship\n</span><span class="Normal-C-C29">  •  Ancestral Shadows -<wbr /> Spirits and Politics in Jung’s Secret life\n</span>', 'CG Jung, Goethe & The Politics of the Spirit : Ancestors, Mediums and Lovers', 'Pellentesque habitant morbi tristique senectus et netus et malesuada fames ac turpis egestas. Vestibulum tortor quam, feugiat vitae, ultricies eget, tempor sit amet, ante. Donec eu libero sit amet quam egestas semper. Aenean ultricies mi vitae est. Mauris placerat eleifend leo.', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '1506-autosave-v1', '', '', '2016-07-17 15:05:33', '2016-07-17 15:05:33', '', 1506, 'http://gmswebdesign.net/spiritual1/2016/07/17/1506-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(2025, 1, '2016-07-18 04:54:31', '2016-07-18 04:54:31', '<p style="text-align: justify;">Your life can change dramatically and quickly. Ancestral Lineage Clearing. is a guided trance work that facilitates clients in removing blocks and patterns that have been in families for generations. Once removed, these patterns are not carried into future generations. Gain new perspectives and coping abilities that help clients get more enjoyment from their lives and with their families.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"></p>\r\n\r\n<h4 style="text-align: justify;">Does the past control your life and hold you back?</h4>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Ancestral Lineage Clearing is an advanced healing technique where a person energetically travels back into their family’s past to change a non-harmonious or dysfunctional pattern in order to bring more happiness, health, joy, prosperity or better relationships into their present life.</p>', 'Is it possible to change past dynamics?', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'feb-20th-ireland', '', '', '2016-09-21 07:10:41', '2016-09-21 07:10:41', '', 0, 'http://gmswebdesign.net/spiritual1/?p=2025', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(2026, 1, '2016-07-18 04:54:31', '2016-07-18 04:54:31', '<p class="Wp-Normal2-P"><span class="Normal2-C-C2">Deep Memory Process Introduction workshop and Evening talk</span><span class="Normal2-C"> -<wbr /> also 1 to 1 sessions available</span></p>\r\n<p class="Wp-Normal-P"><span class="Normal-C-C14">Contact </span><span class="Normal-C-C15">Helen Hennessy  tel 086 3492345    hennessy.holistic@gmail.com</span></p>', 'Feb 20th Ireland', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '2025-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-07-18 04:54:31', '2016-07-18 04:54:31', '', 2025, 'http://gmswebdesign.net/spiritual1/2016/07/18/2025-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(2028, 1, '2016-07-18 04:59:03', '2016-07-18 04:59:03', '<h3>Our Ancestor’s Karma</h3>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Our ancestors are not necessarily more enlightened or evolved, than they were when they lived on Earth, but they’re still capable of having a profound positive or negative impact on our lives.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Their energy resides within all of us and has the\r\npotential to\r\ninfluence us in our daily lives through their living consciousness.\r\nWhen our ancestors were alive, they had their own programming, patterns, beliefs, attitudes and desires that were what created their own Karmic imprinting. Even after their death, all of those energies were still present, but there was no longer a vehicle by which to express them, since the soul was no longer in a physical human body on the physical plane.</p>', 'JULY 23 & 24 United Kingdom', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'july-23-24-united-kingdom', '', '', '2016-10-24 21:39:57', '2016-10-24 21:39:57', '', 0, 'http://gmswebdesign.net/spiritual1/?p=2028', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(2029, 1, '2016-07-18 04:59:03', '2016-07-18 04:59:03', '<p class="Wp-Normal-P"><span class="Normal-C-C10">HEALING ANCESTRAL PATTERNS</span></p>\r\n<p class="Wp-Normal-P"><span class="Normal-C-C10">Transforming generational burdens &amp; neuroses</span></p>\r\n<p class="Wp-Normal-P"><span class="Normal-C-C10">With Juanita Puddifoot &amp; Leo Rutherford</span></p>\r\n<p class="Wp-Normal-P"><span class="Normal-C-C21">We carry in our bodies the stories of our ancestors, their illnesses, tragedies, pain, and grief. The energy of these old family wounds affects us in everyday life .We often see patterns of abuse, incest, addiction, poor health and many other traits passed down through generations.</span></p>\r\n<p class="Wp-Normal5-P"><span class="Normal5-C">Contact: Juanita  tel +01234 350313 email juanitac@btopenworld.com</span></p>\r\n<p class="Wp-Normal5-P"><span class="Normal5-C">Or Richard Diss tel  01525-<wbr />862278    email   Richard@clophillcentre.co.uk</span></p>', 'JULY 23 & 24 United Kingdom', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '2028-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-07-18 04:59:03', '2016-07-18 04:59:03', '', 2028, 'http://gmswebdesign.net/spiritual1/2016/07/18/2028-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(2030, 1, '2016-07-18 04:59:37', '2016-07-18 04:59:37', '<p class="Wp-Normal5-P"><span class="Normal5-C">THE STAR MAIDEN’S CIRCLE with Leo Rutherford and Juanita Puddifoot</span></p>\r\n<p class="Wp-Normal5-P"><span class="Normal5-C-C0">The Circle unravels our life issues, shows us the source of them and guides us to potent places where we can effect change. It shows how we tend to get caught in the powerlessness of chasing our own tail, our own limiting patterns and habits. It then challenges us to free ourselves from those old patterns and change our future.</span></p>\r\n<p class="Wp-Normal5-P"><span class="Normal5-C-C0">The work is powerful and touches the deep wounds within to bring insights and change.</span></p>\r\n<p class="Wp-Normal5-P"><span class="Normal5-C">Contact: Juanita  tel +01234 350313 email juanitac@btopenworld.com</span></p>\r\n<p class="Wp-Normal5-P"><span class="Normal5-C">Or Richard Diss tel  01525-<wbr />862278    email   Richard@clophillcentre.co.uk</span></p>', 'JUNE 25th/26th  United Kingdom', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'june-25th26th-united-kingdom', '', '', '2016-09-21 06:55:15', '2016-09-21 06:55:15', '', 0, 'http://gmswebdesign.net/spiritual1/?p=2030', 0, 'post', '', 0),
