(2032, 1, '2016-07-18 05:00:06', '2016-07-18 05:00:06', '<p class="Wp-Normal-P" style="text-align: justify;"><span class="Normal-C-C19">Dynamic release and healing the Body</span></p>\r\n<p class="Wp-Normal-P" style="text-align: justify;"><span class="Normal-C-C19">Using Angels, Spirit healers, Wise Ones, Ancestors and Power Animals</span></p>\r\n<p class="Wp-Normal-P" style="text-align: justify;"><span class="Normal-C-C19">with Deep Memory Process therapeutic skills</span></p>\r\n<p class="Wp-No-Spacing-P" style="text-align: justify;"><span class="No-Spacing-C">The body is the bridge to enable us to connect more deeply with the illuminated light beings including:-<wbr /> Angels, spirit healers, wise loving ancestors and shamanic power animals.</span></p>\r\n<p class="No-Spacing-P" style="text-align: justify;"><span class="No-Spacing-C"> how to give the physical body a voice to tell its story</span></p>\r\n<p class="No-Spacing-P" style="text-align: justify;"><span class="No-Spacing-C"> how to use props, visualisation, phrases for healing</span></p>\r\n<p class="No-Spacing-P" style="text-align: justify;"><span class="No-Spacing-C"> Learn how to enable yourself and clients to have a physical sense of being healed</span></p>\r\n<p class="No-Spacing-P" style="text-align: justify;"><span class="No-Spacing-C-C0">Contact: Juanita  tel +01234 350313 email juanitac@btopenworld.com</span></p>', 'June 17th, 18th, 19th United Kingdom', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'home-events-workshops-dmp-training-testimonials-articles-archives-contact-free-your-mind-listen-to-your-body-release-your-emotions-and-heal-your-spirit-energy-gateways-natural-health-magazin', '', '', '2016-09-21 06:44:55', '2016-09-21 06:44:55', '', 0, 'http://gmswebdesign.net/spiritual1/?p=2032', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(2033, 1, '2016-07-18 05:00:06', '2016-07-18 05:00:06', '<p class="Wp-Normal-P"><span class="Normal-C-C19">Dynamic release and healing the Body</span></p>\r\n<p class="Wp-Normal-P"><span class="Normal-C-C19">Using Angels, Spirit healers, Wise Ones, Ancestors and Power Animals</span></p>\r\n<p class="Wp-Normal-P"><span class="Normal-C-C19">with Deep Memory Process therapeutic skills</span></p>\r\n<p class="Wp-No-Spacing-P"><span class="No-Spacing-C">The body is the bridge to enable us to connect more deeply with the illuminated light beings including:-<wbr /> Angels, spirit healers, wise loving ancestors and shamanic power animals.</span></p>\r\n<p class="No-Spacing-P"><span class="No-Spacing-C"> how to give the physical body a voice to tell its story</span></p>\r\n<p class="No-Spacing-P"><span class="No-Spacing-C"> how to use props, visualisation, phrases for healing</span></p>\r\n<p class="No-Spacing-P"><span class="No-Spacing-C"> Learn how to enable yourself and clients to have a physical sense of being healed</span></p>\r\n<p class="No-Spacing-P"><span class="No-Spacing-C-C0">Contact: Juanita  tel +01234 350313 email juanitac@btopenworld.com</span></p>', 'Home. Events. Workshops. DMP Training. Testimonials. Articles. Archives. Contact. Free your mind, listen to your body, release your emotions and heal your spirit Energy Gateways Natural Health Magazine  “many have been on Juanita’s workshops before and simply adore her – and with reason, for she has a way of hitting the nail on the head” ....….……………… “Learning how to transform negative emotional energy from past childhood experiences can be an incredibly liberating experience”.  Jini Reddy UK Journalist  Contact For information about consultations click here      For more testimonials ….    +44 (0)1234 350313    Diary of Events 2016 If your group or organisation are interested in having a bespoke workshop or event with Juanita  such as - talks, conferences, workshops or training  dates are available for 2016 so please contact Juanita  to discuss your requirements in more detail.  (click on arrows for more details) Ireland DMP    Feb 20th Ireland Deep Memory Process Introduction workshop and Evening talk - also 1 to 1 sessions available Contact Helen Hennessy  tel 086 3492345    hennessy.holistic@gmail.com  March  frid 4th to 9th  2016 Module 2 - Working with Spirit and Transition Topics:The interlife or ‘Bardo’ phase; unfinished business with persons on earth; life review; reconciliation and forgiveness; integration of soul-fragments, mediation and use of spirit helpers and guides; animal spirits; ancestors; levels of Bardo reality.  Module 3  - Healing the Energy or Subtle Body Topics : Body or postural image; wounds to the etheric body; chronic holding patterns at death; letting the body tell its story; places of stored emotion in the body; strategies for release of body patterns in past lives and the ‘Bardos’. Module 4 - Working with Residues of Trauma and Abuse: Dissociation and the Body Topics: Memory and the body; recognizing clinical “shock”; PTSD and dissociative states; trauma release and catharsis; reactions to sexual and physical abuse, chronic pain, torture and horror; collective unconscious bleed-throughs from “past lives” and wounded “spirit” attachments; patterns of denial and chronic shut-down; healing strategies; dialoguing with the body; working with breath and the body. To graduate as a DMP practitioner there are also practice sessions, personal work, supervision, written case work.(contact Juanita for these)  With Juanita Puddifoot to book - Tel : + 44 (0) 1234 350313   Email juanitac@btopenworld.com   DMP Training           APRIL 9 & 10 Norway  Introduction workshop to Deep Memory Process – transpersonal regression therapy to explore soul wounds from current and past life residues. Join Juanita on this experiential workshop to explore the many lives of your soul. Content covers :- some of the theory behind the process, group and individual exercises, experience a past life memory, demonstration.  Sun 10th April Norway Ancestors and Spirit Release workshop. Come to this one day workshop and learn how to hear our ancestors’ stories especially their unfinished issues. Explore ways of bringing healing and resolution for them including the lost souls who need our compassion and help.  Contact: Eva Foss  tel +47 926 66 300  email fosseva@yahoo.no     NORWAY JUNE 25th/26th  United Kingdom THE STAR MAIDEN’S CIRCLE with Leo Rutherford and Juanita Puddifoot The Circle unravels our life issues, shows us the source of them and guides us to potent places where we can effect change. It shows how we tend to get caught in the powerlessness of chasing our own tail, our own limiting patterns and habits. It then challenges us to free ourselves from those old patterns and change our future. The work is powerful and touches the deep wounds within to bring insights and change. Contact: Juanita  tel +01234 350313 email juanitac@btopenworld.com Or Richard Diss tel  01525-862278    email   Richard@clophillcentre.co.uk     June 17th, 18th, 19th United Kingdom', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '2032-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-07-18 05:00:06', '2016-07-18 05:00:06', '', 2032, 'http://gmswebdesign.net/spiritual1/2016/07/18/2032-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
