(2199, 1, '2016-09-21 07:10:41', '2016-09-21 07:10:41', '<p style="text-align: justify;">Your life can change dramatically and quickly. Ancestral Lineage Clearing. is a guided trance work that facilitates clients in removing blocks and patterns that have been in families for generations. Once removed, these patterns are not carried into future generations. Gain new perspectives and coping abilities that help clients get more enjoyment from their lives and with their families.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"></p>\r\n\r\n<h4 style="text-align: justify;">Does the past control your life and hold you back?</h4>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Ancestral Lineage Clearing is an advanced healing technique where a person energetically travels back into their family’s past to change a non-harmonious or dysfunctional pattern in order to bring more happiness, health, joy, prosperity or better relationships into their present life.</p>', 'Is it possible to change past dynamics?', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '2025-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-09-21 07:10:41', '2016-09-21 07:10:41', '', 2025, 'http://egw.gmswebdesign.net/2016/09/21/2025-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
